\hline Property & f(x)? & \text{Why?} \\ \hline Injective & \checkmark & f(x)\neq f(y) \implies x\neq y \\ \hline Surjective & \checkmark & y\in S\implies x\in\N \\ \hline \end{tabular} \end{align} %text And hence, $f(x)$ is also \underline\text{bijective/invertible}%

